## 10) Recommended Operations Practice
- Keep `STRICT_FEATURE_COMPATIBILITY=true` in production.
- Monitor `/health` and `/api/system/status`.
- Track upload/report/audit endpoints for latency and error rates.
- Use regular backup/restore strategy for MongoDB and uploaded artifacts.
